Package k23b.sa.JobProvider

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IJobProvider
    Provides functionality of reception for jobs to be completed that will be replaced by the Aggregator Manager in Part 2
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JobGenerator
    It generates a large amount of tasks based on a small file specified by the jobFileName property.
    JobReader
    It reads from a large file specified by the jobFileName property returning each and every job in the file gradually.
    LineParser
    Parses the line read from the JobGenerator or JobReader and constructs a Job element which then is returned
    RestJobProvider
    Creates an array of Jobs sent by the AM.
